anoship-mstdf
=============

This distribution includes the MSTDF-AD reference implementation, vendored under
`mstdf_ad/`, so that the methods in the associated publication can be reproduced
in full.

Original work
-------------
"MSTDF-AD: Modeling Spatiotemporal Dependency Fusion for Non-Stationary Time
Series Anomaly Detection." Information Processing & Management, 2026.
https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0306457326002797

Authors: Weikang Shi, Hancheng Xiao, Zhipeng Qiu, Zhixia Zeng, Weifu Zhu,
Shi Zhang, Ruliang Xiao.

Upstream source: https://github.com/Conviss/MSTDF-AD

Inclusion
---------
The `mstdf_ad/` sources are reproduced from the upstream repository (joint work
of the authors listed above) and are included here with the authors' consent for
reproducibility. Only intra-package import paths were adjusted to make the code
importable as the `mstdf_ad` package; the model, training, and evaluation logic
are unchanged from upstream.

